The cardiology and internal medicine departments at Hospital Universitario QuironÂ Salud in Madrid have launched a multidisciplinary consultation for persistent or long COVID-19, aimed at offering specialized care to patients who have overcome COVID-19 infection and continue to show symptoms. Jose Angel Cabrera, chief of cardiology at Quiron University Hospital, explaines the symptoms and impact of long-term COVID-19, saying that it will not only affect the health of individuals but also broader society.